   <conbody>
      <div class="- topic/div ">
         <p class="- topic/p ">The standard UPS system configuration consists of rectifier
modules, inverter modules, a static switch module and a manual bypass
switch module.</p>
         <p class="- topic/p ">Options that can be added are a DC output or
dual rectifier mains for the rectifier modules. With the DC output
it is recommended to add a breaker between the inverter input and
DC output.</p>
         <note class="- topic/note ">The options can also be combined.</note>
